pageContext.claim: “I see Schumer is already criticizing my State of the Union speech, even though he hasn't seen it yet. He’s just upset that he didn't win the Senate, after spending a fortune, like he thought he would. Too bad we weren't given more credit for the Senate win by the media!”
pageContext.analysis: There is little historic about a one-seat gain in the Senate; Republicans had started the session with 52 seats. In fact, given that mostly Democratic seats were up for reelection, in many red seats, the outcome was not unexpected.
